S.FORM: Alassane Dramane Ouattara nilacul u kungku nu zuma cidekay a tademaw u sulit nu Hulam u siwkay niza Alassane Dramane Ouattara(1 a bulad 1 a demiad 1942 a mihcan nalecuhan) ,tatama, u lumeniay a tademaw. u misingkiway atu mikuwanay nu kanatal. u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Cote d'ivoirie ayza sa ci Alassane Dramane Ouattara, micakat a demiad sa i 2010 a mihca 12 bulad 4 demiad. sikawaw ciniza i Abidjan . kakuniza malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government
